				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Just my 2cp on this.<BR>
<BR>
As a Troll Shadow Knight, I favor the 2HS weapon over any 1H weapon.  Over the last few weeks of soloing, I have found that with the same con same mob, wielding the 2HS (Jarseth Battle Sword), I have about a bubble MORE of health at the end of a battle than when I am fighting with my MoSS/Velium shield.  Yes!  <BR>
<BR>
My average damage with the JBS, is around 65 - 75 with my max being 120 (I am level 40 now, so that max may go up)  The best I have seen with the MoSS is mid 60's and the average is in the 35-40 range.
